U.K. Stocks Erase Their Earlier Gain; Benchmark FTSE 100 Is Little Changed

-- B y   P e t e r   L e v r i n g
-- 
2011-06-27T13:04:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/u-k-stocks-erase-their-earlier-gain-benchmark-ftse-100-is-little-changed.html
U.K. stocks erased their gains as
losses in drugmakers and banks overshadowed an advance in food
and drink companies.   The FTSE 100 Index fell less than 0.1 percent to 5,693.12
at 2:03 p.m. in  London , having earlier climbed 0.5 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
